videos.description: David Blough completes an easy pitch-and-catch to Cole Herdman for a 20-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Blough finds a wide open Herdman for Purdue TD

videos.description: Shannon Brooks rips off a long run to set up Minnesota in the red zone.
videos.headline: Brooks breaks off 40-yard run

videos.description: Conor Rhoda completes to Tyler Johnson who dives in for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Rhoda finds Johnson for six

videos.description: P.J. Fleck was disappointed with the turnovers but likes the intensity of his defense.
videos.headline: Fleck wants defense to keep swarming in second half

videos.description: Elijah Sindelar finds D.J. Knox who scampers in for the 22-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Knox catches short pass and does rest for Purdue TD

videos.description: Elijah Sindelar fires a strike to Jared Sparks on the flea flicker for 24 yards.
videos.headline: Purdue goes deep on flea flicker

videos.description: With the game on the line, Ja'Whaun Bentley intercepts a Conor Rhoda pass and sprints 76 yards for the game-clinching TD as Purdue leads 31-17.
videos.headline: Purdue secures victory with pick-six

videos.description: Purdue head coach Jeff Brohm credits his teams' self-belief in their win over Minnesota which saw a long rain delay in a close game.
videos.headline: Coach Brohm sees team effort in victory
